  "body": "Skeleton issue. Awaiting PR.\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want discover screens to look pretty like in the design so that using discover is a delight.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: There are a number of discrepancies between the design and Discover. The goal of this issue is to capture the main ones for: Recent statuses.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31394855-a7554b28-addf-11e7-8390-253456258549.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31394867-aa63da96-addf-11e7-8d78-d973abc2d53c.png)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31394799-81e64e00-addf-11e7-9cb1-1b055d308b09.png)\r\n\r\n#### List of things to fix (non-exhaustive)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Must have\r\n\r\n- [ ] margins from the screen edges should be 16 px (from the chat button to the right edge, 16 px from the left side to an userpick and status)  \r\n- [ ] top status' text has a wrong margin from the top of the card. It should be 16px\r\n- [ ]  the margin between chat button and the bottom of the status' card should 12px\r\n- [ ]  separation lines between statuses should go from the edge to the edge. Check design in zepplin\r\n\r\n## Nice have \r\n- [ ] Name icon not centered\r\n- [ ] Grey background missing\r\n- [ ] Toolbar lack of margin, not centered\r\n- [ ] TEST Chat button missing / style\r\n\r\nProbably more but start for now.",
